response.job_title: Director Of Engineering at Mundi | Ex-Rappi
response.summary:
I am an engineer manager passionate about innovation. I like to work on complex problems that involve optimization and operational efficiency. I love working on problems that require ingenious thinking and have a great impact on society, I also prefer to develop large-scale systems that require better performance and availability to function.

I have managed the following programming languages: Kotlin, Golang, Javascript, Python, PHP, Java, Ruby, R, Haskell, C in different development environments. I have worked in incipient development environments with Monoliths, I have also destroyed one, building microservices proposing architectures that help the scalability of the systems.

The specialties that I have developed are the following: Design and development of information systems, development of mobile applications, database modeling and management, design of programs with artificial intelligence.

My last advantage, I have the ability to learn and teach others to take them to another level in their professional career.
